JET: Oh?

SPIKE: Don't give me that! Why do we have all three neatly gathered here?!

ED: Ed loves Piyokos!

JET: And once again we didn't get any bounty...

FAYE: Hey, wait, you're a girl?

JET: Really, nothing good comes outta Earth!

