Jet takes off in Hammerhead.

FAD: JET!


The prison ship. Tucan mans a gun turret.

TUCAN: I don't know who ya are, but we'll give ya a warm welcome!

He shoots at Hammerhead. Jet dodges the shots. A panel on the prison ship
